		"description": "<p class=\"preFade fadeIn\">At level 6 you gain the ability to alter the very terrain of the battlefield. As a bonus action you can render a 30 foot diameter area within 100 feet difficult terrain for 10 minutes. If you have already created difficult terrain using this feature, that effect is ended when you create new additional terrain.</p>\n<p>If you expend a 3rd-level or higher spell slot when you activate this feature, you may choose one of the following enhancements:</p>\n<ul data-rte-list=\"default\">\n<li>\n<p class=\"preFade fadeIn\">The area of your difficult terrain is 50 feet in diameter.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p class=\"preFade fadeIn\">The area of your difficult terrain is a 100-foot line.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p class=\"preFade fadeIn\">The area of your difficult terrain is a 50-foot cone.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p class=\"preFade fadeIn\">A number of allies equal to your proficiency bonus is unaffected by the difficult terrain.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>",
